  "name": "Morrison COU2 — VAD hemolysis credibility assessment (Minimal profile, no COU)",
  "description": "Minimal-profile UnitOfAssurance for CFD hemolysis prediction of the FDA generic centrifugal blood pump. This package omits hasContextOfUse entirely, leaving the intended-use scope undefined. All 13 credibility factors are populated and a DecisionRecord is present, satisfying MinimalBody SHACL requirements. The absence of a Context of Use means no reviewer can determine the operational envelope, patient population, or device configuration to which the model's predictions are meant to apply.",
