      "acceptanceCriteria": "Version-controlled solver with documented test suite covering all hemolysis model paths; independent code review completed.",
      "rationale": "Solver is version-controlled and unit tests exist for core fluid routines, but hemolysis sub-model test coverage is incomplete and no independent code review has been performed. Achieved level falls below MRL 5 requirement."
    },
