      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
      "requiredLevel": 4,
      "achievedLevel": 1,
      "factorStatus": "not-assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Iterative convergence residuals < 1e-6 for all equations; round-off error bounded; solver error distinguished from discretization error.",
      "rationale": "Solver error not separately characterized. Residual convergence reported at 1e-4; no round-off error analysis performed. Flagged as epistemic gap at MRL 5."
