      "requiredLevel": 4,
      "achievedLevel": 1,
      "factorStatus": "not-assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Documented simulation protocol with independent analyst reproducibility check; user influence on results quantified.",
      "rationale": "No formal simulation protocol or reproducibility study conducted. Analyst-to-analyst variability in mesh generation and boundary condition setup has not been assessed. Epistemic gap at MRL 5."
