      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
      "requiredLevel": 5,
      "achievedLevel": 1,
      "factorStatus": "not-assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Systematic evaluation of hemolysis constitutive model alternatives; model form uncertainty quantified relative to experimental observations.",
      "rationale": "Power-law hemolysis model selected without systematic comparison to alternative formulations (e.g., strain-based or mechanistic red cell damage models). Model form uncertainty not quantified. Critical epistemic gap at MRL 5."
    },
