      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
      "requiredLevel": 5,
      "achievedLevel": 2,
      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "All uncertain input parameters identified; probability distributions assigned from literature or experimental data; Monte Carlo propagation with convergence confirmed.",
      "rationale": "Monte Carlo UQ performed on five input parameters (viscosity, density, power-law exponents, inlet velocity). Distributions assigned from literature but not experimentally calibrated for the target device. Convergence of MC estimator confirmed at N=10000 samples. Achieved level below MRL 5 requirement due to missing experimental calibration."
    },
