      "requiredLevel": 4,
      "achievedLevel": 1,
      "factorStatus": "not-assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Statistical characterization of experimental sample population; inter-laboratory reproducibility of hemolysis measurements documented.",
      "rationale": "Single laboratory provided all experimental hemolysis data. No inter-laboratory comparison performed. Sample-to-sample biological variability in hemolysis susceptibility not characterized. Epistemic gap at MRL 5."
    },
    {
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
      "factorType": "Equivalency of input parameters",
