      "acceptanceCriteria": "Formal equivalency assessment between validation experiment inputs and COU inputs; dimensional analysis or similarity parameters documented.",
      "rationale": "No formal equivalency assessment between FDA pump experimental inputs and intended VAD COU inputs. Reynolds number and specific speed similarity not verified. Epistemic gap at MRL 5."
